        archival optical spectra obtained with UVES/VLT. H i data were
        extracted from the Effelsberg-Bonn H i survey and the Galactic
        All-Sky survey. For selected sight lines we obtained deeper
        follow-up observations using the Effelsberg 100-m telescope.
        \textbackslash Results: Ca ii (Na i) halo absorbers at
